<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٢٨٣ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنِ الْمُجَالِدِ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الشَّعْبِيِّ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَمْ يَأْخُذْ مَسْرُوقٌ عَلَى الْقَضَاءِ رِزْقًا»</span> وَأَخَذَ شُرَيْحٌ "<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>